{"tid":864701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港漁業　對中國無意義　可滅","createTime":"2018-10-16T11:31:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-17T09:22:30.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"82852daf92ea6f44fc7007f9fda346219d8f8623","tid":864701,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T11:31:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1050809857920520193\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1050809857920520193&d=cUe2kGK3L7mzwis%2B9D76sQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=1bf5fefd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1050809857920520193&h=76de91ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1050809857920520193</a><br />\n<br />\n香港漁業，對香港是獨特的，有重要意義，對中國卻不是，中國有幾十個省，幾百個縣，幾千個市。就算這次沒有填海，下次中國政府一規劃下來，還是一樣。當初由中國統戰而來的零丁議席並不會有用，何況現在殖民政府已不用在乎議會一兩票。"},{"pid":"6e393543fab7e830a6c46bc92ba9e3a0cca38668","tid":864701,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T09:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}